<P>
DOG KILLS SLEEPING MASTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A bull terrier attacked its master while he was asleep and bit through his 
throat, killing him, police in the western Siberian town of Omsk said Tuesday. 
The man's wife found her husband dead with the bull terrier sitting calmly 
alongside. She called police, who took the dog outside and shot it. 
</P>
