<TEXT>
<P>
 The public is invited to a Neighborhood Watch program meeting scheduled for 
Sept. 12 in the City Council chambers, 33282 Street of the Golden Lantern. 
</P>
<P>
 The guest speaker will be Assistant Sheriff Doug Storm, a 20-year veteran of 
the department who has experience in combatting gangs and drug suppression. 
</P>
