<P>
 OFF: 3 DEF: 3 04,26,05,05,05 TOP RETURNERS OFF DEF YR Raoul Apodaca, 5-11, 170 
-- DB Sr. Sonje Berg, 6-2, 175 QB -- Sr. Eric Garcia, 5-11, 200 C -- Sr. Juan 
