 OFF: 5 DEF: 4 04,28,05,05,05 TOP RETURNERS OFF DEF YR Aaron Brown, 5-9, 170 -- 
LB Sr. Mike Critchfield, 6-1, 180 -- DB Sr. Jeff Fewel, 5-10, 225 G -- Sr. 
