QB FS Sr. Tim Jones, 5-11, 198 RB LB Sr. Trevor Ray, 6-0, 190 TE LB Sr. 
04,29,05,05,05 TOP NEWCOMERS OFF DEF YR Dave Barrios, 5-6, 175 FB LB Jr. 
