<DOCNO> LA083194-0119 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 074747 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
August 31, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 3; Metro Desk 
</P>
