 Pipeline construction hours will be limited to 9 a.m. to 3 p.m., Monday 
through Friday, Dunbar said. 
</P>
<P>
 One of the pipes being replaced is a 24-inch pipeline, one of the district's 
main supply routes that provides water to homes and businesses in South Laguna 
and Dana Point. 
</P>
